# ============================================================
# Prenatal Factors and Trio PGS Analysis
# ============================================================
#
# This script evaluates associations between prenatal factors, trio-based
# polygenic scores (PGSs), and ASD-related phenotypes in discovery and
# replication cohorts. It includes:
#   1) Logistic models for prenatal factors as outcomes.
#   2) Linear trio models for ASD-related quantitative phenotypes.
#   3) Sensitivity analyses excluding or adjusting for prenatal factors.
#   4) Interaction analyses between prenatal factors and trio PGSs.
#   5) Fixed-effect meta-analysis across discovery and replication cohorts.
#
# Replace the file paths below with project-specific paths before running.

